# Optional: private visitor stats in Google Analytics 4 (free for typical portfolio traffic).
# 1. Create a GA4 property: https://analytics.google.com → Admin → Data streams → Web → add divijmuthu.github.io
# 2. Copy the Measurement ID (looks like G-XXXXXXXXXX).
# 3. Put it in .env.local for local builds, or set GitHub Actions variable GA_MEASUREMENT_ID (see README).
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=
